  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LIU_MIN_YING_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PROTECT_SUPPLIES.title": "出手护营",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LIU_MIN_YING_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PROTECT_SUPPLIES.description": "获得50金币。受到5点不可格挡伤害。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LIU_MIN_YING_EVENT.pages.DISTRIBUTE_SUPPLIES_RESULT.description": "你分出一部分粮草，营地里的气氛安定了不少。临走时，你也觉得自己更能扛事了。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LIU_MIN_YING_EVENT.pages.PROTECT_SUPPLIES_RESULT.description": "你赶走了趁乱而来的恶徒，流民凑出些报酬塞给你。只是混战里你也挨了几下。",

