  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PICK_OLD_WEAPON.description": "失去50金币。从3张随机铜色武器牌中选择1张获得。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PREPARE_FOR_BATTLE.title": "备战待敌",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PREPARE_FOR_BATTLE.description": "失去6点不可格挡伤害。升级1张攻击牌。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.LEAVE.title": "转身离开",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.LEAVE.description": "什么也不做。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_BING_QI_PU_EVENT.pages.PICK_OLD_WEAPON_RESULT.description": "你挑了一件趁手的旧兵器。它不新，却明显还没到该被遗忘的时候。",
