  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GU_ZHAN_CHANG_EVENT.title": "古战场",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GU_ZHAN_CHANG_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.description": "荒草之间，断戟残甲半埋土中。风吹过时，像有旧日喊杀声从地底翻起。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GU_ZHAN_CHANG_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PICK_WEAPON.title": "拾起兵刃",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GU_ZHAN_CHANG_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.PICK_WEAPON.description": "受到5点不可格挡伤害。获得1张随机铜色武器牌。",
