  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LU_YU_SHAN_ZEI_EVENT.pages.FORCE_THROUGH_RESULT.description": "你硬闯了过去，身上也难免挂彩。好在那群人终究没能拦住你。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LU_YU_SHAN_ZEI_EVENT.pages.STALL_FOR_TIME_RESULT.description": "你一边敷衍周旋，一边趁乱顺走了点东西，总算没白吃这口亏。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_LU_YU_SHAN_ZEI_EVENT.pages.NOT_ENOUGH_GOLD.description": "你翻遍钱袋也凑不出他们要的数。山贼们显然并不满意。",

