  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GUAN_FU_ZHAO_MU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.description": "官道旁贴着新告示，几名差役正在招募敢战之人。他们看中了你的身手，递来一枚令牌。",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_GUAN_FU_ZHAO_MU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.options.MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_RELIC_ZHENG_ZHAO_LING_RELIC.title": "接受征召",
