  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_ZHENG_ZHAO_RU_WU_EVENT.pages.NOT_ENOUGH_GOLD.description": "你摸了摸钱袋，发现自己连脱身的钱都拿不出来。",

  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_YI_ZHUANG_BI_YU_EVENT.title": "义庄避雨",
  "MY_FIRST_ST_S2_MOD_EVENT_YI_ZHUANG_BI_YU_EVENT.pages.INITIAL.description": "雨势渐急，你在山脚下看见一座破旧义庄。门板半掩，屋檐滴水不断。",
